  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Fred w. Heslewood, national or\nganizer of the Industrial Workers\nof the World, was arrested in Occur\nd'Alene yesterday on a charge of\ncriminal conspiracy in connection\nwith the local free speech fight.\n\n\nHeslewood is fighting extradition.\nHe was taken into custody by Cap\ntain of Detectives M. J. Burns.\nChief of Police Sullivan and Prose-\ncutting Attorney Pugh were present\nThe officers held requisl,lon from\nGovernor Hay calling on the Idaho\nauthorities to deliver up the pris-\nToner.\n\n\nHeslewood is being held in Occur\ndAlene pending the return of the\nextradition papers from Governor\nBrady of Idaho."
    }
  ]
